      "_doc": "NIST SARD Juliet Java Test Suite v1.3 \u2014 112 CWEs, ~28k test cases. Mirror by UnitTestBot. Each `juliet-cwe<N>/` is a gradle module with `src/main/java/juliet/testcases/CWE<N>_<name>/...` test files. Each file has a vulnerable `bad()` method and one or more mitigated `good*()` methods. Ground truth derived from directory CWE; bench scores per-family.",
